Now that both backend and frontend are running with the new CRM color scheme, I will proceed to build the custom React frontend:

**Frontend Implementation Plan:**
- Create Zustand store for CRM state (`src/stores/crmStore.ts`)
- Create TypeScript types for CRM entities (`src/types/crm_types.ts`)
- Create API service for CRM endpoints (`src/api/crmApi.ts`)
- Build CRM pages and components:
  - ContactsPage: List/add/edit/delete contacts, assign tags
  - TagsPage: List/add/delete tags
  - CampaignsPage: Create campaigns, view campaign history, send emails by tag
- Use shadcn/ui components for all UI elements
- Integrate authentication flow (login/signup, protected routes)
- Add toast notifications for user feedback

**Next: Create CRM TypeScript types for frontend.**

